Dialogue: 100,0:00:02.11,0:00:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}E în regulă, ați făcut destule. Mersi.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Era grupul lui Kino?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:09.24,0:00:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:10.61,0:00:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Au făcut căutări, dar n-au putut \Ngăsi Distrugătorul lui Chise.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.87,0:00:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nici măcar o bucățică din el, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:17.04,0:00:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei bine, după acea explozie de artilerie...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:20.25,0:00:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:21.83,0:00:25.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probabil nu te deranjează, \Ndar o voi spune oricum.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:25.71,0:00:27.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu este vina ta.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:30.76,0:00:34.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Credeam că ne vor bombarda baza apoi, dar, dintr-un oare care motiv, nu au făcut-o.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.47,0:00:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bătălia de astăzi a fost cel mai probabil doar un test de tragere.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:39.81,0:00:41.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am pierdut patru oameni în \Nacea "test de tragere", nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:42.02,0:00:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Odată finalizat, nu vor mai fi doar patru oameni,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.19,0:00:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ci întreaga Republică va fi distrusă.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.15,0:00:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu prea contează asta pentru noi, dar mă îndoiesc că domnișoara maior va lăsa asta să se întâmple.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:51.45,0:00:52.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce este?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.24,0:00:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nimic.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.45,0:00:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oricum, noua mașinărie \Neste tăcută, deocamdată.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îți poți da seama de asta?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-am memorat vocea.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.79,0:01:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și mă îndoiesc că va trage din nou spre noi, comandantul inamic.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-am găsit.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.46,0:01:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pe fratele tău?!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.67,0:01:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar și el m-a găsit pe mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.80,0:01:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Va veni după mine de data asta.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.01,0:01:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta e perfect pentru mine, \Ndar norocul vostru s-a cam terminat.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce veți face?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.02,0:01:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vă veți spânzura astă-seară \Nca să nu muriți mâine?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nicio șansă.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:26.44,0:01:30.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te vom urma până la capăt, Zeu al Morții.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.79,0:03:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noi vom fi cu toții nimiciți.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.66,0:03:08.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asta este unitatea pentru exterminare.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.83,0:03:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ordine speciale...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.13,0:03:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ținta: Zona cea mai \Nadâncă din teritoriul Legiunii.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.30,0:03:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Durata misiunii: Fără limită. \NNiciun fel de sprijin...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eliminarea imediată în caz de retragere?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:22.39,0:03:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Această unitate a fost creată \Nca noi să luptăm până murim.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:25.81,0:03:28.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acesta este capătul drumul pentru noi.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vom muri cu toții aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce s-a întâmplat, Lena?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.99,0:03:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}O misiune finală fără șanse de supraviețuire, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.29,0:03:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiar sună a ceva ce s-ar pune \Nîn aplicare în această țară.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.79,0:03:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ajută-mă, te rog!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trebuie să facem ceva!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:56.09,0:03:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să facem ceva?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:57.26,0:03:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce anume, mai exact?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.18,0:04:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să apărem la televizor ținând un discurs?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:00.89,0:04:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Să găsim pe cineva și să țipăm la el?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.93,0:04:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă asta le-ar fi schimbat gândirea, nu s-ar fi ajuns aici.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.14,0:04:11.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-ți mai bate capul. Știi foarte bine că nu-i putem ajuta.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.56,0:04:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Orice vom face va fi în zadar, deci...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:13.98,0:04:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Încetează!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:15.73,0:04:19.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu te mai preface că ești o persoană rea doar ca să ai o scuză să nu faci nimic!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tu ești cea care trebuie să înceteze!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.08,0:04:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E destul...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.83,0:04:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vorbesc serios.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu putem face nimic!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:31.21,0:04:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu putem face absolut nimic ca să-i salvăm!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.38,0:04:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Annette...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.59,0:04:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vecinii de vizavi erau savanți în echipa de cercetare a tatălui meu.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:45.51,0:04:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Familiile noastre erau apropiate.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar totul s-a schimbat când a început războiul.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.44,0:04:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vecinii noștri erau... rezidenți ai Districtului 86.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aveau doi băieți.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.03,0:05:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fratele mai mare era cu câțiva ani mai mare, dar cel mic era de vârstă cu mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.16,0:05:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mergeam la aceeași școală și ne jucam o grămadă.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.41,0:05:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eram prieteni.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.08,0:05:17.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar următorul lucru pe care l-am observat a fost că toți rezidenții Districtului 86 au încetat să mai vină la școală.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:17.34,0:05:20.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar colegii mei de clasă începuseră să se ia de mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.55,0:05:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Au spus că eram prietenă cu un colorat spurcat.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-a durut! Dar nu puteam face nimic!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.47,0:05:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și totuși, el nu a știut nimic și tot a venit să se joace cu mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.98,0:05:36.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-am refuzat și am ajuns să ne certăm.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar atunci i-am spus-o...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.40,0:05:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ești un colorat spurcat!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi era frică.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.62,0:05:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îmi era frică de mine că am reușit să spun așa ceva.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.20,0:05:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:52.25,0:05:57.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When my dad was thinking about\N taking them in, despite the danger,
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I didn't want to.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:59.13,0:06:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am spus că nu era prietenul meu. Am spus că nu vreau să mă pun în pericol pentru el.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.51,0:06:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cred că tatăl meu voia sprijinul meu atunci.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.26,0:06:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar eu i-am oferit o cale de scăpare.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.06,0:06:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar ei au fost trimiși în lagăre în următoarea zi.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:17.31,0:06:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tot ce am putut face a fost să-mi spun că nu-i puteam ajuta.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Că nu puteam face absolut nimic pentru ei.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.74,0:06:28.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar tu... Tu mereu...
Dialogue: 100,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ascultă, Lena.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.08,0:06:35.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te poți purta ca o sfântă,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dar ești la fel de vinovată ca și mine.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ce este acest loc?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:51.01,0:06:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Copiii și mama lor de vizavi aveau o putere ciudată.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:56.64,0:07:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Știau ce simt fiecare fără să vorbească.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatăl meu a devenit interesat de acea putere.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar aici a început totul.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mai întâi, își puneau aceste dispozitive care arată ca niște jucării
Dialogue: 100,0:07:11.95,0:07:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,și încercau să ghicească ceea ce gândea mama lor în spatele perdelei.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:15.71,0:07:18.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Experimentele erau ca un joc.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar când armata a aflat că exista
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.88,0:07:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,o nouă metodă de comunicare care ar putea înlocui-o pe cea fără fir,
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.01,0:07:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,i-au ordonat tatălui meu s-o perfecționeze, cu orice preț.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Iar rezultatul a fost...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.22,0:07:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dispozitivul RAID pe care-l folosești.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:34.60,0:07:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ai idee câți rezidenti ai Districtului 86 au murit ca să fie perfecționat?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:39.94,0:07:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu poți folosi animale din moment ce trebuie să transmită cuvinte, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.19,0:07:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vrei să spui că...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exact. Experimente pe oameni.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.03,0:07:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cu toții spunea că rezidenții \NDistrictului 86 nu erau oameni.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teribil de convenabil, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toți subiecții de test erau copii.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rezultatele pe primul loc. Siguranța pe ultimul.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cu toții au murit în chinuri.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.92,0:08:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tatăl meu nu a mai putut trăi cu faptele sale, așa că s-a sinucis.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu a fost un accident?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.42,0:08:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crezi că dintre toate persoanele, tatăl meu ar greși setările Para-RAID-ului?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:11.26,0:08:16.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mereu îmi spunea că și-a abandonat prietenii și a provocat multă suferință.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și că el, mai mult decât oricine altcineva, \Nmerită să moară în chinuri.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.23,0:08:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă ceea ce a spus el e adevărat, nu sunt și eu vinovată că mi-am abandonam prietenul?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.23,0:08:28.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De asta am preluat cercetările sale, victime și tot!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.49,0:08:32.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Groparul" îl chema, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.95,0:08:36.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Îți amintești că ni s-a cerut să investigăm deoarece acel supervizor s-a sinucis, nu?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.91,0:08:37.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Da...
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.79,0:08:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dacă l-ar fi adus pe Procesorul care a provocat acele decese,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,aș fi putut să-l salvez măcar pe el.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:44.59,0:08:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar asta e doar o ipocrizie.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:46.46,0:08:49.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mă bucur că acei idioți, care se ocupau de transport, au refuzat să-l aducă.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vezi? Puteam spune că nu 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.43,0:08:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't save anyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:55.43,0:08:58.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're no different!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.31,0:09:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're even worse!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.60,0:09:06.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You interfered and kept them alive, \Nand now they're being ordered to die!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:07.86,0:09:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd just slacked off and let them die,
Dialogue: 100,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they would've never had to carry out those orders.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now they will, thanks to you!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.12,0:09:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Te urăsc, Lena.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.71,0:09:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never show your face to me again.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu-i voi lăsa să moară.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone else die.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.71,0:10:10.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.25,0:10:15.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me cancel the special recon orders \Ngiven to Spearhead!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.01,0:10:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you not to get too involved.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is insane!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.39,0:10:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why must they advance into enemy territory\Nuntil they die, for no reason?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:24.52,0:10:27.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Eighty-Six all need to die.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:28.40,0:10:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what's best for the country,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.98,0:10:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,according to its government, \Nand indirectly, its people.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:34.28,0:10:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the will of the nation.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:38.16,0:10:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If what we've done to the Eighty-Six\N gets out at the end of the war,
Dialogue: 100,0:10:44.29,0:10:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Republic will become a pariah state
Dialogue: 100,0:10:47.58,0:10:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and remembered forever as oppressors.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:51.67,0:10:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And to keep that from happening...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.05,0:10:57.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's why you've forbidden the\Nrecovery and burial of their dead.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:58.34,0:11:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With their deaths, it would be as if they've never existed.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:03.39,0:11:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And thus, the Republic\N will have done nothing wrong.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.77,0:11:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A select few will know the whole truth.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the vast majority either turn a blind eye,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:13.82,0:11:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,don't care, or tacitly support it.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:17.91,0:11:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And our job as the army, Lena, \Nis to follow the people's wishes.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:23.16,0:11:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Eighty-Six are citizens no matter the race!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:26.46,0:11:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Republican ideals that Saint Magnolia\N expounded should protect them, too!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:31.04,0:11:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they aren't, how can this \Nbe the will of the Republic?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a country full of fools and villains,
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.38,0:11:43.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who executed Saint Magnolia for the \Nsake of their own wealth and greed.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What can you expect of them?!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:49.65,0:11:55.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Humans are not ready for the\Npure ideals of freedom and equality.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.61,0:11:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I doubt we'll ever be.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:57.90,0:12:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just saying that to justify your despair!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's wrong to sit back and let this happen!
Dialogue: 100,0:12:04.29,0:12:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're free to speak of your hopes and ideals,
Dialogue: 100,0:12:07.45,0:12:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you won't persuade anyone.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:10.25,0:12:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you came to me in the first place, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:14.59,0:12:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, hope and despair are the same.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:17.38,0:12:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wishing for something you can't attain.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:19.93,0:12:23.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're two sides of the same coin.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:30.90,0:12:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Captain Nouzen, I have a set of special recon orders.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:34.19,0:12:35.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've received them.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:38.32,0:12:41.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:43.74,0:12:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to obey these ridiculous orders.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Run away.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To where?
Dialogue: 100,0:12:52.00,0:12:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone dies eventually.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:54.46,0:12:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't blame someone just\N because that day came a little early.
Dialogue: 100,0:12:58.46,0:13:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you always just accept it?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:04.39,0:13:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've lost your future, your wishes,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:05.85,0:13:07.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and soon, even your life...
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.39,0:13:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you don't hate us?\N How is that possible?!
Dialogue: 100,0:13:14.65,0:13:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Major, we're not going there to die.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:21.57,0:13:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're finally following the path \Nwe wanted to follow,
Dialogue: 100,0:13:25.37,0:13:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to the place we wanted to go.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A place where we can finally be free.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't trample our will with your pity.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:33.67,0:13:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then... Then at least avoid fighting.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'll be impossible.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:39.42,0:13:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll need to fight to move forward.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've known that from the start.
Dialogue: 100,0:13:50.02,0:13:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll need to fight to kill your brother, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:13:56.65,0:13:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do you always pick up on these things?
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.03,0:14:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can tell...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:02.44,0:14:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sad, but you still laugh coldly
Dialogue: 100,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when you talk about your brother.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't fight, please.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:12.16,0:14:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he's part of the Legion, \Nyou can't fight your brother.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My brother is a Shepherd.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't go anywhere without killing him.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:18.13,0:14:18.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 100,0:14:18.92,0:14:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Major...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no need to monitor us anymore.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:23.80,0:14:24.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean—
Dialogue: 100,0:14:24.63,0:14:28.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want you to hear my brother's last words.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:28.85,0:14:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please don't contact us again.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.14,0:14:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beyond the eastern border,\NI can't hear the Legion's voices.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.82,0:14:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anyone's still out there, they're your best bet.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.70,0:14:49.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When a Shepherd dies, \Nthe Legion is thrown into chaos for a little while.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can buy you that much time.
Dialogue: 100,0:14:52.87,0:14:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:54.75,0:14:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Captain Nouzen...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must survive until then.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's it looking?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:30.32,0:15:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Provisions, fuel, ammo, \Nand spare parts are all packed.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:36.41,0:15:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I also packed extra spares for the legs, \Nfor a certain idiot commander.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:40.92,0:15:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:42.63,0:15:45.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can do simple repairs yourself, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:15:45.51,0:15:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I break them a lot.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Act a little ashamed, you brat!
Dialogue: 100,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't fight like you usually do.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That, I can't promise.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.68,0:15:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the last time, just lie and agree.
Dialogue: 100,0:15:59.48,0:16:00.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:01.19,0:16:02.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really are...
Dialogue: 100,0:16:18.21,0:16:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for Haruto.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:20.25,0:16:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he'd lasted a little longer, \Nhe could've gone for a fun hike.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:24.09,0:16:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think the rain'll stop?
Dialogue: 100,0:16:26.92,0:16:29.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice to have clear skies, \Nat least for the first day.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:29.76,0:16:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know a trick! Kaie used to do it!
Dialogue: 100,0:16:33.43,0:16:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kids! Come 'ere.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:42.73,0:16:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that it's the last time, \NI think I'm gonna miss the old man's lectures.
Dialogue: 100,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:48.50,0:17:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 100,0:17:52.38,0:17:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We all gathered here on the first day, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:55.80,0:17:56.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean when we were assigned?
Dialogue: 100,0:17:56.89,0:17:57.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 100,0:17:57.72,0:18:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we all swore to each other again.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:04.44,0:18:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"No matter who calls us pigs, \Nwe'll never let ourselves become one."
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.40,0:18:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Even if we're the last one, \Nwe'll fight until the last day."
Dialogue: 100,0:18:15.78,0:18:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the end, the five of us survived.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:18.33,0:18:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:22.83,0:18:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Major never did call again.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:26.17,0:18:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, missing her already?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.63,0:18:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it does kind of bug me, though.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:32.80,0:18:36.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all the time we've spent together, \Nshe could've said goodbye.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:36.76,0:18:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, like that.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:38.51,0:18:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We told her a million times to leave us alone, \Nand she finally got it, is all.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rain stopped.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Clear skies!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trick worked, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:18:50.32,0:18:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a good omen!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, look!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:54.36,0:18:55.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're all shiny!
Dialogue: 100,0:18:55.95,0:18:58.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I cleaned all your marks, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:18:58.41,0:19:00.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're nice and clean, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cool!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's happy?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:04.25,0:19:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was filthy.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm happy for you.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:16.72,0:19:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:17.84,0:19:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Snacks.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:19.34,0:19:20.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 100,0:19:23.72,0:19:26.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He treated us like kids until the end.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:31.52,0:19:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody forgot anything, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:19:34.28,0:19:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:35.24,0:19:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 100,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:38.45,0:19:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin.
Dialogue: 100,0:19:41.87,0:19:43.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:38.11,0:21:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to protect you.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:44.24,0:21:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yet I...
Dialogue: 100,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:50.54,0:21:56.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Brother, are Mom and Dad not coming back?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:56.42,0:21:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why?
Dialogue: 100,0:21:57.34,0:22:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was barely keeping myself together back then.
Dialogue: 100,0:21:57.63,0:22:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I can't hear Mom's voice.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:00.30,0:22:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Brother, why did Mom die?
Dialogue: 100,0:22:06.43,0:22:08.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's your fault!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:07.47,0:22:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:08.22,0:22:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mom went to fight because of you!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:10.93,0:22:12.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}You killed her.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:14.23,0:22:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:15.48,0:22:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's your fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:16.40,0:22:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:17.44,0:22:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:20.11,0:22:21.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:21.44,0:22:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That Mom and Dad died. \NThe fact that I'm about to die.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:24.91,0:22:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's all your fault,
Dialogue: 100,0:22:28.33,0:22:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shin!
Dialogue: 100,0:22:31.66,0:22:32.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 100,0:22:38.38,0:22:42.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't handle my hatred and rage\Nthat I felt at my own powerlessness,
Dialogue: 100,0:22:42.96,0:22:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, your brother will protect you forever.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:46.64,0:22:48.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the person I was supposed to protect.
Dialogue: 100,0:22:58.48,0:23:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nu te-am putut proteja.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:03.32,0:23:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dar...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:06.15,0:23:07.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:11.74,0:23:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Acum vom fi împreună pentru totdeuna.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:16.08,0:23:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vin după tine.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:18.04,0:23:20.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Și o voi face fără corpul meu fragil de om.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:21.84,0:23:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,De data asta, fratele tău te \Nva proteja pentru totdeuna.
Dialogue: 100,0:23:27.18,0:23:28.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Deci...
Dialogue: 100,0:23:29.97,0:23:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vino la mine. Shin!
Dialogue: 100,0:23:36.48,0:23:37.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Adio.
